prize was awarded in 1984 to Marcel and Claude B. Auguste for their
work <em>L‚Äôexp√©dition Leclerc, 1801‚Äì1802</em> and the second prize to
Emmanuel Justin Castra for his work entitled, <em>Aux origines de la
