history prize resumed in partnership with the Fondation Roger
Gaillard. Since the award‚Äôs return, historians D√©lide Jospeh and
Jean Alix Ren√© won in 2015 and 2017, respectively.¬†<a href="#fnref:15" class="reversefootnote" role="doc-backlink">&#x21a9;&#xfe0e;</a></p>
